npx spago init&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add npm script in &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;package.json&lt;/code&gt; and install dependencies with &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;npm install&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
